title: Plat 2 Adc LF>Established plat + team, available for tryouts
body: Ask me anything! Ill tell you my playstyle, cs @ 10, laning etc.

replies.body:
I am a Silver 5 support main (I don't think you are interested in me though haha).  But do you play aggressively (i.e. level 2 all in)?  Which champions do you main?  What is your CS count in 10 minutes?  Thanks :)

Feel free to let me know that you are not interested.
